cellular network algorithm for smoother network connections.\nApps\nAdds the app icon for Tips to the Home screen. Discover more interesting features now!\nYou can now perform fuzzy searches that include spaces in Settings.\nYou can now search for app names in Settings to quickly view app details or manage the app.\nAdds the Breeno Memory feature. You can swipe up with 3 fingers to add screen content to the app as a memory. The app can also analyze and summarize the memories for you, as well as archive them as collections.\nAdds the Mind mapping feature in Documents. It allows you to generate mind maps with one tap, and export them to Photos or share them.\nIntroduces Game Camera, which provides Live screenshots and Flashback recording to help you capture your epic gaming moments.\nOptimizes the display order of search results in Settings.\nMultimedia\nAdds the Track Splitter feature, which allows for the adjustment of volume for vocals and background sounds in music.\nAdds the Speaker cleaner feature which can clean speakers and ensure optimal speaker performance. You can change the settings for this feature in &quot;Phone Manager - Tools - More - Accessibility &amp; convenience - Speaker cleaner&quot;.\nSystem\nAdds the option to wake Breeno in system navigation. You can change the settings for this feature in &quot;Settings - System &amp; update - System navigation&quot;.\nThe system can now actively trigger an interception when apps installed through non-secure sources require sensitive permissions.\nAdds an option to reduce white point, which enhances the comfort level of people with color sensitivity. This option is available in &quot;Settings - Accessibility &amp; convenience - Accessibility - Vision - Reduce white point&quot;.\nImproves the floating bar responsiveness of floating windows.\nImproves the animation when exiting Quick Settings and the Notification drawer for better responsiveness and smoother transitions.\nYou can now seamlessly open an app from quick functions when the screen is locked.\nWhen notifications are stacked, the latest notification will now display a summary showing the number of undisplayed notifications and their sources.\nImproves the keyboard layout for more convenient operations and more appealing visuals.\nImproves the color effect of the navigation bar background and app icons in some scenarios for better consistency of colors.\nImproves the Recent tasks feature, which now supports more apps to run in the background.\nIntegrates the June 2025 Android security patch to enhance system security.","companyName":null,"fileSize":10410006486,"softwareVersion":"15.0.0.833(CN01)","projectNo":"23101","host":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com","nvFileInfo":[{"nv":"nv_10010111","path":"/dfs/25/06/28/200aec3086614e7b8572286043a62637.zip","md5":"fd5472036323f63700f554a851786503","size":1727831670,"taskId":"up-id-f2726d76-cad1-4f47-a1d7-4cd225cd1ee5"},{"nv":"common","path":"/dfs/25/06/28/8400e6c3bf484a86ba6e1746a7521429.zip","md5":"83a8158940a6f82b21e02535bdf39921","size":8681637501,"taskId":"up-id-424eec6d-5e4e-4f8b-9533-5087f8454e3a"},{"nv":"nv_00000000","path":"/dfs/25/06/28/2a58d44a58824ca588f7d8d5343ba8e0.zip","md5":"fd5472036323f63700f554a851786503","size":1727831670,"taskId":"up-id-fba055be-bc73-4cb5-b31f-e67c6e97dd6c"}]},{"inSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/06/27/1cde3b9d17a94aacbab86f5bd6aeb385.zip","outSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/06/27/1cde3b9d17a94aacbab86f5bd6aeb385.zip","marketModel":"OPPO Find X8","updateDesc":null,"googlePatchDate":"2025/06/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PKB110domestic_11_15.0.0.832CN01_2025053020040170.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/23series/23101_15.0.2_V/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP1/PKB110domestic_11_15.0.0.832CN01_2025053020040170.zip","filePath":"/dfs/25/06/27/1cde3b9d17a94aacbab86f5bd6aeb385.zip","fileName":"PKB110domestic_11_15.0.0